column2: SELECT   TOP # A.ra,A.dec,B.distance,A.objID,B.objID as objIDMatch,A.specobjID,C.specobjID as specobjIDJOIN,D.specobjID as specobjIDClean FROM   SpecPhotoAll AS A   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(A.ra,A.dec,#/#.) AS B   LEFT JOIN SpecPhotoAll as C on B.objID=C.objID   LEFT JOIN SpecObj as D on C.specobjID=D.specobjID INTO    MyDB.SpecMatch
